<#
.SYNOPSIS
    Microsoft consumer experiences must be turned off.

.NOTES
    Author          : Luis Chavez
    Date Created    : 2025-07-09
    Last Modified   : 2025-07-09
    Version         : 1.0
    CVEs            : N/A
    Plugin IDs      : N/A
    STIG-ID         : WN10-CC-000197

.TESTED ON
    Date(s) Tested  :
    Tested By       :
    Systems Tested  :
    PowerShell Ver. :

.USAGE
    PS C:\> .\remediate-WN10-CC-000197.ps1
#>

# Ensure policy path
New-Item -Path "HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\CloudContent" -Force | Out-Null

# Turn off consumer experiences
Set-ItemProperty -Path "HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\CloudContent" `
    -Name "DisableWindowsConsumerFeatures" -Type DWord -Value 1
